14a6adb8fc68615d434a95d7","tid":1027583,"uid":60139,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:50:01.000Z","msg":"有，米撚亂試"},{"pid":"80e8fe6ebb302425d980cc1af0eb69697c6e9a02","tid":1027583,"uid":60279,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"9d62606ea899cbd22b29f646f2e6bee03e9508ff","tid":1027583,"uid":20189,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:49:22.000Z","msg":"試過，跟住有半年冇野做<br />\n<br />\n頭三個月爽到仆街，去下旅行，日日同唔同fd食飯，自己一個揸本書去cafe睇下，去海邊望下海咁<br />\n<br />\nhea完三個月後開始搵工，搵左兩個月都搵唔到個人就開始慌，係咁問自己係咪咁撚廢，點解份份工見完都冇回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩最後都搵到份叫做ok既工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:53:29.000Z","msg":"同你完全一樣<br />\n<br />\n後來再RESIGN, 好彩果一個月內就搵到幾份好工<br />\n最記得有一次, 問我新聞有關既野, <br />\n第一次咁感欣平時有睇新聞, 先答得到咁得體 最後都請左<br />\n重要加佢2000佢都再比OFFER, 不過我無要到"},{"pid":"601a1fa09e547ac562802ac0c238f92376267769","tid":1027583,"uid":45018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:57:09.000Z","msg":"碎料黎啫，最緊要搵到份自己岩"},{"pid":"f6ff7c2a0e18280d50137ee84b95baa114da9311","tid":1027583,"uid":91897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"601a1fa09e547ac562802ac0c238f92376267769","tid":1027583,"uid":45018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:57:09.000Z","msg":"碎料黎啫，最緊要搵到份自己岩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"岩....返左份伏工個幾月, 上司閪, benefit 返左1星期先同我講做夠一年先可以享用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，今日遞信，聽日見工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336f7cda40fafecd34d0b01d8de6374fc717fdfe","tid":1027583,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:00:10.000Z","msg":"睇你咩行業，窄既真係無搵唔到，坐翻半年等閒事，除非你轉行"},{"pid":"fc88ddaf04f417d1a04089cc0851223e3e66c153","tid":1027583,"uid":9887,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T03:29:08.000Z","msg":"幾份都係裸辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次一個月內搵到，可能當時junior人工低易搵<br />\n第二次hea左3個月先搵，中間有做下parttime，最後搵左兩三個月先搵到，嗰排好驚，見好多份都唔請，我直頭減人工見第二行，最後好彩搵返份本行<br />\n第三次，因為想去半個月旅行所以祼辭，結果返黎搵左一個月一份工都冇得見，可能人工高左冇乜工in，當時好慌因爲結左婚開支大左，最後搵左兩個月見左3份有1份請左"},{"pid":"d3c7056383cd732a92e023be34a5e1b3aa880112","tid":1027583,"uid":53588,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"尋日辭左 hea 返幾個月先<br />\n作為社會既垃圾 是但揾份工唔難 <br />\n上進少少咁多部隊 考中1個都夠過世"},{"pid":"256d493a8c8324711a3f831fe98cfb72c4d85eb3","tid":1027583,"uid":61207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:58:43.000Z","msg":"無儲開錢唔好亂試<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90be2613af079f0ffb9da58736df6fa8a044417","tid":1027583,"uid":2736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96418a92fd0cace233d6bde553c97c1a4ba9f75f","tid":1027583,"uid":44815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"次次祼辭都休息幾個月先搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2932bd5d6dc6c750d16d4109bed779daf31f703a","tid":1027583,"uid":84040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:41:51.000Z","msg":"經常性祼辭，通常一返工覺得唔對路就會即走"},{"pid":"f8b0225a63e3abcb807a1c2f7feca9d3f8a6ae07","tid":1027583,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲未搵得返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e63e928eedbe41ea945711d570a81dd974dcad","tid":1027583,"uid":164582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:12:58.000Z","msg":"我做過5-6份工<br />\n幾乎份份裸辭<br />\n<br />\n如果你裸辭係想hea 番一頭半個月<br />\n我勸你唔好亂嚟"},{"pid":"229a8041d95cca648f9a517dfac54a1a0a6e6265","tid":1027583,"uid":42762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"